  44:main.c        **** /*******************************************************************************
  45:main.c        **** * Function Name: main
  46:main.c        **** ********************************************************************************
  47:main.c        **** *
  48:main.c        **** * Summary:
  49:main.c        **** *  Main function performs following functions:
  50:main.c        **** *   1. Declares date and time structure and fill it with the initial values
  51:main.c        **** *   2. Enables global interrupts
  52:main.c        **** *   3. Sets initial time and date values
  53:main.c        **** *   4. Sets alarm date, time and mask
  54:main.c        **** *   5. Sets interval mask
ARM GAS  C:\Users\Admin\AppData\Local\Temp\ccsWpz4j.s 			page 3


  55:main.c        **** *   6. Sets DST start and stop configuration
  56:main.c        **** *   7. Prints current date and time values.
  57:main.c        **** *   8. Afterwards, device is continuosly switched to the Sleep low power mode.
  58:main.c        **** *      When the 1PPS event occurs device wakes up, ISR is executed and device
  59:main.c        **** *      is switched to the Sleep mode again till the next 1PPS event.
  60:main.c        **** *      For more information refer to the device TRM and System
  61:main.c        **** *      Reference Guide.
  62:main.c        **** *
  63:main.c        **** *   The information on the display is updated in the ISR.
  64:main.c        **** *
  65:main.c        **** * Parameters:
  66:main.c        **** *  None
  67:main.c        **** *
  68:main.c        **** * Return:
  69:main.c        **** *  None
  70:main.c        **** *
  71:main.c        **** *******************************************************************************/
  72:main.c        **** int main()
